        // Get the current date and time
        const currentDate = new Date();

        // Get elements with class 'promoBanner1' and 'promoBanner2'
        const plaidPromoBanner1 = document.querySelectorAll('.plaidPromoBanner1');
        const plaidPromoBanner2 = document.querySelectorAll('.plaidPromoBanner2');

        if (currentDate >= toggleDate) {
            // Disable .promoBanner1 and enable .promoBanner2
            plaidPromoBanner1.forEach(element => element.classList.add('hidden'));
            plaidPromoBanner2.forEach(element => element.classList.remove('hidden'));

            // Enable .promoBanner1 and disable .promoBanner2
